or:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Accuracy\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Focus\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Fairness\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Integrity\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Commitment\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Our Marketing &amp; Advertising Team\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:32|text_align:left|color:%23000000\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][ultimate_modal icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^162|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Marketing-Team-Alan-Koh.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Marketing-Team-Alan-Koh|description^null\" modal_title=\"Alan Koh  Principal Trainer / International Speaker\" modal_on=\"image\" btn_img=\"id^162|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Marketing-Team-Alan-Koh.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Marketing-Team-Alan-Koh|description^null\" modal_size=\"block\" overlay_bg_opacity=\"80\" img_size=\"80\"]\r\n<blockquote>If your business is not on the Internet, your business will be out of business.</blockquote>\r\nAlan Koh, the Principal Trainer at Impossible Marketing, could not agree more with the above quote from Bill Gates, as he believes that being online helps companies to increase visibility and reduce operating costs.\r\n\r\nAlan is a former banker from Standard Chartered Bank that won multiple awards before he quit his job to pursue his entrepreneurship journey in 2009. He started 11 businesses in the next four years, but all of them failed and nearly wiped out all his savings. While reflecting on his experience, he realised all his previous 11 businesses were unsuccessful as he was unable to attract enough customers. That inspired him to build a business that can solve the issue.\r\n\r\nIn 2012, he started Impossible Marketing with the vision of providing affordable digital marketing services to help companies get targeted traffic, quality leads and sales online. The results were overwhelming, and the team started to grow. In 2013, he converted Impossible Marketing to a private limited company offering digital marketing services and training programs to companies and individual who wish to excel.\r\n\r\nHis story was recently featured in The Sunday Times:\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-163\" src=\"http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Sunday-Times-featuring-Alan-Koh-300x122.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"122\" />[/ultimate_modal][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_section][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][ultimate_modal icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^164|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Serene-marketing-team.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Serene-marketing-team|description^null\" modal_title=\"Serene  Trainer / Business Development Manager\" modal_on=\"image\" btn_img=\"id^164|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Serene-marketing-team.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Serene-marketing-team|description^null\" modal_size=\"block\" overlay_bg_opacity=\"80\" img_size=\"80\"]\r\n<blockquote>A man who stops advertising to save money is like a man who stops the clock to save time.</blockquote>\r\nSerene, a former private banker, is currently a business development manager and trainer at Impossible Marketing. She believes digital marketing advertising is the next big thing and strongly agrees with the above quote by Henry Ford.\r\n\r\nSerene mainly assists Alan in growing Impossible Marketing by undertaking a variety of tasks. Just like Alan, she is also certified directly by Google &amp; Yahoo/Bing.\r\n\r\nShe also holds a Banking &amp; Finance Degree from the Universityof London.[/ultimate_modal][vc_custom_heading text=\"Serene  Trainer / Business Development Manager\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:14|text_align:center|color:%23000000|line_height:1\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][ultimate_modal icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^165|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Lynn-marketing-team.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Lynn-marketing-team|description^null\" modal_title=\"Serene  Trainer / Business Development Manager\" modal_on=\"image\" btn_img=\"id^165|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Lynn-marketing-team.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Lynn-marketing-team|description^null\" modal_size=\"block\" overlay_bg_opacity=\"80\" img_size=\"80\"]\r\n<blockquote>People do not buy goods &amp; services. They buy relations, stories &amp; magic.</blockquote>\r\nLynn is the lead strategist at Impossible Marketing and agrees with the above quote from Seth Godin. She graduated with an RMIT degree in Business Management. An avid teh-o peng person, she loves a good game of squash on the weekends to unwind.\r\n\r\nHaving studiedBusiness IT diploma during her polytechnic years, Lynn has many years of experience in the industry. Now armed with an extensive web and mobile development portfolio built over the past 7 years, Lynn specialises in helping businesses increase their online revenues with conversion optimisation.Her ability to strategise quickly and customise solutions has set her apart in the industry.Lynns core expertise is in recognising different user behaviours and understanding why people do what they do, allowing her to create customised solutions that can attract users attention.[/ultimate_modal][vc_custom_heading text=\"Lynn  Trainer / Lead Strategist\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:14|text_align:center|color:%23000000|line_height:1\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][ultimate_modal icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^166|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Andy-Ecommerce-Trainer.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Andy-Ecommerce-Trainer|description^null\" modal_title=\"Andy  Trainer\" modal_on=\"image\" btn_img=\"id^166|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Andy-Ecommerce-Trainer.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Andy-Ecommerce-Trainer|description^null\" modal_size=\"block\" overlay_bg_opacity=\"80\" img_size=\"80\"]\r\n<blockquote><b>Never depends on a single source of revenue.</b></blockquote>\r\nAndy was from one of the pioneer teams in Groupon Singapore (now known as Fave). During his stay as a senior account manager from 2010 to 2014, he has achieved more than SGD $3million in sales. In 2015, he left Groupon to start his own e-commerce business. He brought in different products from China and sold them on e-commerce platforms such as Groupon, Q10, Carousell, Shopee and Buy 123. The business grew rapidly. In 2016, he set up a warehouse in China to cope with the rising demand. In 2017, he expanded his business to Taiwan.\r\n\r\nSince his e-commerce entrepreneurship journey, Andy has sold more than SGD $1.5 million worth of products in Singapore alone.\r\n\r\nHe loves the above-mentioned quote from Warren Buffett now works at Impossible Marketing as an e-commerce trainer to help individuals who are keen to start their online business and work from home or anywhere in the world.[/ultimate_modal][vc_custom_heading text=\"Andy  Trainer\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:14|text_align:center|color:%23000000|line_height:1\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][ultimate_modal icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^167|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Jeffery-Marketing-Team.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Jeffery-Marketing-Team|description^null\" modal_title=\"Jeffery  Lead Strategist\" modal_on=\"image\" btn_img=\"id^167|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Jeffery-Marketing-Team.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Jeffery-Marketing-Team|description^null\" modal_size=\"block\" overlay_bg_opacity=\"80\" img_size=\"80\"]\r\n<blockquote><strong>Doing business without advertising is like winking at a girl in the dark. You know what you are doing, but nobody else does.</strong></blockquote>\r\nJeffery, formerly a banker, is one of our lead strategists at Impossible Marketing. He graduated from Murdoch with a Bachelor of Business in Economics and Finance (Double Major) and is an enthusiastic athlete who loves going for long distance slow running during his free time.\r\n\r\nAgreeing with the above quote from Steuart Henderson Britt, Jeffery is passionate about digital marketing and believes that every company should seek to enhance their presence online. With his past experience in banking and a passion for digital marketing, he has the ability to understand every clients problems and provide a clear digital solution for their company needs.[/ultimate_modal][vc_custom_heading text=\"Jeffery  Lead Strategist\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:14|text_align:center|color:%23000000|line_height:1\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][ultimate_modal icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^168|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Adeline-marketing-team-276x300.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Adeline-marketing-team-276x300|description^null\" modal_title=\"Adeline  Project Manager / Web Developer\" modal_on=\"image\" btn_img=\"id^170|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Adeline-marketing-team-276x300-1.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Adeline-marketing-team-276x300|description^null\" modal_size=\"block\" overlay_bg_opacity=\"80\" img_size=\"80\"]\r\n<blockquote><strong>The best spot to hide a dead body is page 2 of Google.</strong></blockquote>\r\nAdeline graduated with a Diploma in Interactive Media Informatics from Temasek Polytechnic. With 8 years of experience in web technologies and digital marketing, she is currently the SEO project manager of Impossible Marketing.\r\n\r\nAdeline loves to explore and learn new skills. She believes all businesses must have an online presence in todays digital world, especially on Google search.\r\n\r\nHer main role is to bring clients website to the 1<sup>st</sup>page of Google search for higher visibility and<strong>lead generation</strong>.[/ultimate_modal][vc_custom_heading text=\"Adeline  Project Manager / Web Developer\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:14|text_align:center|color:%23000000|line_height:1\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][ultimate_modal icon_type=\"custom\" icon_img=\"id^169|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Joanne-marketing-team.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Joanne-marketing-team|description^null\" modal_title=\"Joanne  Project Manager\" modal_on=\"image\" btn_img=\"id^169|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Joanne-marketing-team.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^Joanne-marketing-team|description^null\" modal_size=\"block\" overlay_bg_opacity=\"80\" img_size=\"80\"]\r\n<blockquote><strong>Great content deserves great ranking.</strong></blockquote>\r\nJoanne has been with Impossible Marketing since 2013 and she is the 1<sup>st</sup>employee of Impossible Marketing. She loves the process of building a website from scratch, to see it climb in ranking from nowhere to be found on the 1st page of Google search results.\r\n\r\nJoanne is also the SEO project manager. Just like Adeline, she focuses on optimising clients website to the 1st page of Google organic search results.[/ultimate_modal][vc_custom_heading text=\"Joanne  Project Manager\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:14|text_align:center|color:%23000000|line_height:1\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section]', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2018-08-24 04:48:52', '2018-08-24 04:48:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost/impossible/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
