(13, 1, '2018-08-21 07:07:59', '2018-08-21 07:07:59', '[vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" content_placement=\"middle\" parallax=\"content-moving\" parallax_image=\"121\"][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" content_placement=\"middle\" parallax=\"content-moving\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Lead Generation Services in Singapore\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:48|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff|line_height:8\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" parallax_content=\"parallax_content_value\" bg_color_value=\"#000000\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left; color: #ffffff;\">You have a great product and offer an excellent service. Whats next? Does the market know about your products and services?</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left; color: #ffffff;\">Having an outstanding product/service is not enough to grow your business. Apart from brand awareness, you will need customers to buy your companys products and services. Let us bring you 1 step closer!</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: left; color: #ffffff;\">Impossible Marketing is a<a title=\"Digital Marketing Agency Singapore, Digital Marketing Company\" href=\"https://www.impossible.sg/\">Digital Marketing company</a>that focuses on lead generation for companies in Singapore. In short, we bring targeted traffic and quality leads to your website.</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1535087200520{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><strong>Lead generation</strong>is the process of determining and converting potential customers that are interested in a companys products or services. By finding out your companys leads, you can target your marketing strategies towards them, increasing the potential for sales. Our lead generation services ensure that your company can reap the maximum benefits through the array of strategies we employ to direct leads to your website. As one of the top B2B (business-to-business) companies in Singapore, we strive to help our clients achieve their goals of gaining more sales through lead generation.</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Our Lead Generation Services\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:32|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff|line_height:4\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1535087999282{background-color: #000000 !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][interactive_banner_2 banner_title=\"Search Engine Optimization (SEO)\" banner_image=\"id^46|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Digital-Marketing-Singapore-SEO-Services.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Digital-Marketing-Singapore-SEO-Services|description^null\" banner_style=\"style5\" banner_min_height_op=\"custom\" banner_title_bg=\"#ffffff\" banner_color_title=\"#000000\" banner_color_bg=\"#ffffff\" image_opacity=\"0.8\" image_opacity_on_hover=\"0.8\" banner_title_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" banner_title_font_size=\"desktop:18px;\" banner_min=\"400\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][interactive_banner_2 banner_title=\"Search Engine Marketing (Pay Per Click)\" banner_image=\"id^47|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Online-Marketing-PPC-and-SEM-Agency.png|caption^null|alt^null|title^Online-Marketing-PPC-and-SEM-Agency|description^null\" banner_style=\"style5\" banner_min_height_op=\"custom\" banner_title_bg=\"#ffffff\" banner_color_title=\"#000000\" banner_color_bg=\"#ffffff\" image_opacity=\"0.8\" image_opacity_on_hover=\"0.8\" enable_responsive=\"yes\" responsive_min=\"768\" responsive_max=\"900\" banner_title_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" banner_title_font_size=\"desktop:18px;\" banner_min=\"400\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][interactive_banner_2 banner_title=\"Social Media Marketing\" banner_image=\"id^48|url^http://localhost/impossible/wp-co