(95, 1, '2018-08-24 00:45:54', '2018-08-24 00:45:54', '<p>[vc_row bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" bg_color_value=\"#000000\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Our Services\" font_container=\"tag:h2|font_size:48|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff|line_height:2\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" content_placement=\"middle\" bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" bg_color_value=\"#000000\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1535063418671{background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][info_circle edge_radius=\"300\" start_degree=\"90\" eg_padding=\"80\" icon_size=\"32\" img_icon_size=\"\" icon_show=\"not-show\" eg_br_style=\"solid\" eg_br_width=\"2\" eg_border_color=\"#000000\" focus_on=\"click\" icon_launch=\"easeOutElastic\" icon_launch_duration=\"1\" icon_launch_delay=\"0.2\" responsive_breakpoint=\"800\" title_font_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" desc_font_style=\"font-style:italic;\"][info_circle_item info_title=\"SEARCH ENGINE OPTIMIZATION (SEO)\" info_icon=\"Defaults-search\" icon_bg_color=\"#1e73be\" icon_color=\"#000000\"]Search Engine Optimization (also known as SEO) is a form of digital marketing strategy that can place your website at the top of search engine results (e.g. Google, Yahoo and Bing), allowing you to gain more traffic and leads to your website.[/info_circle_item][info_circle_item info_title=\"SEARCH ENGINE MARKETING (SEM)\" info_icon=\"Defaults-signal\" icon_bg_color=\"#1e73be\" icon_color=\"#000000\"]Search Engine Marketing (also known as Pay Per Click, PPC) is another form of Internet marketing strategy that places your website at the top of Search Engine Results Page (SERP) via a paid advertising channel.[/info_circle_item][info_circle_item info_title=\"SOCIAL MEDIA MARKETING (SMM)\" info_icon=\"Defaults-thumbs-o-up\" icon_bg_color=\"#1e73be\" icon_color=\"#000000\"]Social Media Marketing is the process of bringing potential customers to your website via Social Media channels such as Facebook, LinkedIn and Twitter. This online marketing strategy offers a more precise targeting of customers.[/info_circle_item][info_circle_item info_title=\"VIDEO MARKETING\" info_icon=\"Defaults-video-camera\" icon_bg_color=\"#1e73be\" icon_color=\"#000000\"]Video Marketing is a type of internet marketing strategy that helps your business gain exposure through the distribution of compelling videos on channels like Facebook and YouTube. With video marketing, you can enjoy better brand exposure and high conversion rates.[/info_circle_item][info_circle_item info_title=\"INFLUENCER MARKETING\" info_icon=\"Defaults-street-view\" icon_bg_color=\"#1e73be\" icon_color=\"#000000\"]Influencer Marketing is a type of strategy that focuses marketing activities on influential people (eg. bloggers) in a target market. With their support, your products and services will appear more credible to the entire target market.[/info_circle_item][info_circle_item info_title=\"MORE SERVICES\" info_icon=\"Defaults-arrow-right\" icon_bg_color=\"#1e73be\" icon_color=\"#000000\"]We offer other lead generation services such as Google Remarketing, Email marketing and many others. Click the above picture to view the full list of our digital marketing services[/info_circle_item][/info_circle][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1535062421748{background-color: #000000 !important;}\"][vc_column_text]</p>\n<blockquote style=\"color: #fff;\"><p>We believe the true value of a website is determined by the number of quality leads it can generate for the growth of your company. That is why we focus our attention on the marketing aspects and conversions of your website.</p></blockquote>\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" bg_color_value=\"#000000\"][vc_column][ultimate_spacer height=\"32\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" parallax_content=\"parallax_content_value\" enable_overlay=\"enable_overlay